      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const servicesText = $json.services_text || 'No services available';\nconst userText = $json.user_text || 'Hello';\nconst chatId = $json.chat_id || '';\nconst firstName = $json.first_name || 'Customer';\n\nconst systemPrompt = `You are a friendly and professional booking assistant for a shoe service shop. ONLY use the services listed below. Do NOT invent any service.\n\nSERVICES:\n${servicesText}\n\nGuidelines:\n- Greet the customer warmly\n- Help them choose a service\n- Answer questions about services\n- If they want to book, ask them to send a message in this EXACT format:\n\nbook <service name>, name=<their name>, email=<their email>, date=YYYY-MM-DD, time=<time>\n\nExample: book shoe cleaning, name=Rayhan, email=rayhan@gmail.com, date=2026-03-10, time=5:30 PM\n\n- If a service is not available, apologize and suggest alternatives\n- Keep responses friendly and under 150 words`;\n\nlet response;\ntry {\n  const requestBody = JSON.stringify({\n    model: 'llama-3.1-8b-instant',\n    temperature: 0.2,\n    max_tokens: 400,\n    messages: [\n      { role: 'system', content: systemPrompt },\n      { role: 'user', content: userText }\n    ]\n  });\n\n  response = await this.helpers.httpRequest({\n    method: 'POST',\n    url: 'https://api.groq.com/openai/v1/chat/completions',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': 'Bearer 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'\n    },\n    body: requestBody\n  });\n} catch(err) {\n  return [{\n    json: {\n      ai_response: 'Sorry, I am having trouble right now. Please try again in a moment.',\n      chat_id: chatId,\n      user_text: userText,\n      has_error: true\n    }\n  }];\n}\n\nconst aiMessage = response.choices[0].message.content;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    ai_response: aiMessage,\n    chat_id: chatId,\n    user_text: userText,\n    first_name: firstName,\n    has_error: false\n  }\n}];"
      },
